description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Beginner Yoga Flow' from the channel Owen Henn.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow vibe.
The The Zen Flow vibe means Grounding, intentional, breath-centered, unhurried. This is especially good for When you need balance, mindfulness, and release..
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Let yourself relax and have fun with Owen in Miami in this beginner friendly  yoga flow. ...
